<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Auto-Record - Panel del Chofer</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/img/google.ico">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-800">

    <header class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-900 via-blue-700 to-sky-500 text-white shadow-lg">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <img src="/img/LogoProyecto.jpeg" alt="Logo Auto-Record" class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full object-cover border-2 border-white shadow-md">
                <div>
                    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-wide">Auto-Record</h1>
                    <p class="text-sm text-blue-100">Panel operativo del chofer</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <nav class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 text-sm md:text-base font-medium">
                <a href="/" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-white/15 transition">Inicio</a>
                <a href="/funciones" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-white/15 transition">Funciones</a>
                <a href="/descargas" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-white/15 transition">Descargas</a>
                <a href="/nosotros" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-white/15 transition">Nosotros</a>
                <a href="/informacion" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-white/15 transition">Información</a>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
        <section class="mb-10">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-lg border border-blue-100 p-8">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Panel del Chofer</h2>
                <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">
                    Bienvenido(a), <strong class="text-blue-800"><%= user?.name || "Usuario" %></strong>. Desde este panel puedes consultar tu ruta, visualizar tu operación reciente y reportar incidencias durante tu jornada.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- FILA 1 -->
        <section class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8">

            <!-- HISTORIAL -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-lg border border-blue-100 p-8">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-2">Historial de rutas recientes</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">Consulta tus últimos registros de servicio.</p>

                <div class="overflow-x-auto">
                    <table class="w-full min-w-[650px] text-left border-collapse">
                        <thead>
                            <tr class="bg-slate-100 text-slate-700 text-sm">
                                <th class="px-4 py-3 rounded-l-xl">Fecha</th>
                                <th class="px-4 py-3">Ruta</th>
                                <th class="px-4 py-3">Horas</th>
                                <th class="px-4 py-3 rounded-r-xl">Estado</th>
                            </tr>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody class="text-slate-700">
                            <tr class="border-b border-slate-200">
                                <td class="px-4 py-4">10/12/2025</td>
                                <td class="px-4 py-4">Ruta 3 - Centro</td>
                                <td class="px-4 py-4">06:00 - 14:00</td>
                                <td class="px-4 py-4">
                                    <span class="inline-block bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 text-sm font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">
                                        Completada
                                    </span>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr class="border-b border-slate-200">
                                <td class="px-4 py-4">09/12/2025</td>
                                <td class="px-4 py-4">Ruta 3 - Centro</td>
                                <td class="px-4 py-4">06:15 - 13:50</td>
                                <td class="px-4 py-4">
                                    <span class="inline-block bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 text-sm font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">
                                        Completada
                                    </span>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td class="px-4 py-4">08/12/2025</td>
                                <td class="px-4 py-4">Ruta 3 - Centro</td>
                                <td class="px-4 py-4">06:00 - 12:30</td>
                                <td class="px-4 py-4">
                                    <span class="inline-block bg-sky-100 text-sky-700 text-sm font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">
                                        Incidencia
                                    </span>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- TU RUTA -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-lg border border-blue-100 p-8">
                <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 mb-6">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-2">Tu ruta asignada</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600">Información principal de tu servicio actual.</p>
                    </div>
                    <span class="inline-block bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-full">
                        En servicio
                    </span>
                </div>

                <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-4">
                    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-blue-100 bg-slate-50 p-5">
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">Ruta</p>
                        <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Ruta 3 - Centro</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-blue-100 bg-slate-50 p-5">
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">Horario</p>
                        <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">6:00 - 14:00</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="rounded-2xl border border-blue-100 bg-slate-50 p-5 mb-4">
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">Paradas principales</p>
                    <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800">Terminal Norte / Plaza Central / Mercado Sur</p>
                </div>

                <div class="rounded-2xl border border-blue-100 bg-slate-50 p-5">
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">Observación</p>
                    <p class="text-slate-700 text-lg">
                        Mantén actualizado tu estado y reporta cualquier incidencia para mejorar la coordinación del servicio.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- FILA 2 -->
        <section class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8">

            <!-- MAPA -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-lg border border-blue-100 p-8">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 mb-6">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-2">Mapa de ruta</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600">Visualiza tu trayecto y la ubicación operativa.</p>
                    </div>
                    <span class="inline-block bg-sky-100 text-sky-700 text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-full">
                        En seguimiento
                    </span>
                </div>

                <div class="w-full rounded-3xl overflow-hidden border border-blue-100 bg-slate-50">
                    <div id="map" class="w-full h-[380px]"></div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- REPORTAR INCIDENCIA -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-lg border border-blue-100 p-8">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-800">Reportar incidencia</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600">Registra cualquier evento durante tu jornada.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <form class="incident-form space-y-5">
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Tipo de incidencia</label>
                        <select class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-blue-200 bg-slate-50 px-4 py-4 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-400">
                            <option>Seleccionar tipo de incidencia</option>
                            <option>Falla mecánica</option>
                            <option>Accidente menor</option>
                            <option>Problema de tránsito</option>
                            <option>Otro</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Descripción</label>
                        <textarea
                            rows="5"
                            placeholder="Describe brevemente lo ocurrido..."
                            class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-blue-200 bg-slate-50 px-4 py-4 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-400"
                        ></textarea>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Ubicación (opcional)</label>
                        <input
                            type="text"
                            placeholder="Ej. Av. Juárez y Calle 5"
                            class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-blue-200 bg-slate-50 px-4 py-4 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-400"
                        >
                    </div>

                    <button
                        type="button"
                        class="w-full bg-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-800 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-4 rounded-2xl shadow-md transition btn-primary"
                    >
                        Guardar registro
                    </button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- FILA 3 -->
        <section class="flex justify-end">
            <div class="w-full lg:w-[48%] bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-700 to-sky-600 text-white rounded-3xl shadow-lg p-8">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Conduce con mejor seguimiento</h3>
                <p class="text-blue-100 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
                    Auto-Record te permite mantener el control de tu jornada, registrar incidencias con rapidez y consultar tu operación reciente para mejorar la comunicación con el área de supervisión.
                </p>

                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
                    <a href="/auth/logout"
                    class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 rounded-2xl bg-white text-blue-800 font-semibold shadow-sm hover:bg-slate-100 transition">
                        Cerrar sesión
                    </a>

                    <a href="/"
                    class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 rounded-2xl border border-white/30 text-white font-semibold hover:bg-white/10 transition">
                        Ir al inicio
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="bg-slate-950 text-slate-200 mt-12">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-6 text-center text-sm">
            TechHive Labs 2025 • Gestión inteligente de transporte público
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script>
        function initMap() {
            const centro = { lat: 20.2767, lng: -97.9611 };

            const map = new google.maps.Map(document.getElementById("map"), {
                center: centro,
                zoom: 14,
                mapTypeControl: false,
                streetViewControl: false,
                fullscreenControl: true
            });

            new google.maps.Marker({
                position: centro,
                map: map,
                title: "Ubicación actual del chofer"
            });
        }
    </script>

    <script
        async
        defer
        src="https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/js?key=<%= googleMapsApiKey %>&callback=initMap">
    </script>

    <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>